<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="и®ӯз»ғ">и®ӯз»ғ
  <a href="/tutorials/machine-learning/torch/5-03-dropout/#и®ӯз»ғ" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
</h2>

<p>и®ӯз»ғзҡ„ж—¶еҖҷ, иҝҷдёӨдёӘзҘһз»ҸзҪ‘з»ңеҲҶејҖи®ӯз»ғ. и®ӯз»ғзҡ„зҺҜеўғйғҪдёҖж ·.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">optimizer_ofit</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">torch</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">optim</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Adam</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">net_overfitting</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">(),</span> <span class="n">lr</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.01</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">optimizer_drop</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">torch</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">optim</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Adam</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">net_dropped</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">(),</span> <span class="n">lr</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.01</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">loss_func</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">torch</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">MSELoss</span><span class="p">()</span>

<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">t</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">500</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">pred_ofit</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">net_overfitting</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">pred_drop</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">net_dropped</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">loss_ofit</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">loss_func</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">pred_ofit</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">y</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">loss_drop</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">loss_func</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">pred_drop</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">y</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">optimizer_ofit</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">zero_grad</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">optimizer_drop</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">zero_grad</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">loss_ofit</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">backward</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">loss_drop</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">backward</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">optimizer_ofit</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">step</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">optimizer_drop</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">step</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="еҜ№жҜ”жөӢиҜ•з»“жһң">еҜ№жҜ”жөӢиҜ•з»“жһң
  <a href="/tutorials/machine-learning/torch/5-03-dropout/#еҜ№жҜ”жөӢиҜ•з»“жһң" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
</h2>

<p>еңЁиҝҷдёӘ <code class="highlighter-rouge">for</code> еҫӘзҺҜйҮҢ, жҲ‘д»¬еҠ дёҠз”»жөӢиҜ•еӣҫзҡ„йғЁеҲҶ. жіЁж„ҸеңЁжөӢиҜ•ж—¶, иҰҒе°ҶзҪ‘з»ңж”№жҲҗ <code class="highlighter-rouge">eval()</code> еҪўејҸ, зү№еҲ«жҳҜ <code class="highlighter-rouge">net_dropped</code>, <code class="highlighter-rouge">net_overfitting</code> ж”№дёҚж”№е…¶е®һж— жүҖи°“.
з”»еҘҪеӣҫеҶҚж”№еӣһ <code class="highlighter-rouge">train()</code> жЁЎејҸ.</p>

<p><a href="/static/results/torch/5-3-1.gif">
 <img class="course-image lazy-img" src="/static/results/torch/5-3-1.gif" alt="Dropout зј“и§ЈиҝҮжӢҹеҗҲ" title="Dropout зј“и§ЈиҝҮжӢҹеҗҲ" />
</a></p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>    <span class="o">...</span>

    <span class="n">optimizer_ofit</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">step</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">optimizer_drop</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">step</span><span class="p">()</span>

    <span class="c1"># жҺҘзқҖдёҠйқўжқҘ
</span>    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">t</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="mi">10</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">:</span>     <span class="c1"># жҜҸ 10 жӯҘз”»дёҖж¬Ўеӣҫ
</span>        <span class="c1"># е°ҶзҘһз»ҸзҪ‘з»ңиҪ¬жҚўжҲҗжөӢиҜ•еҪўејҸ, з”»еҘҪеӣҫд№ӢеҗҺж”№еӣһ и®ӯз»ғеҪўејҸ
</span>        <span class="n">net_overfitting</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="nb">eval</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">net_dropped</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="nb">eval</span><span class="p">()</span>  <span class="c1"># еӣ дёә drop зҪ‘з»ңеңЁ train зҡ„ж—¶еҖҷе’Ң test зҡ„ж—¶еҖҷеҸӮж•°дёҚдёҖж ·.
</span>
        <span class="o">...</span>
        <span class="n">test_pred_ofit</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">net_overfitting</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">test_x</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">test_pred_drop</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">net_dropped</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">test_x</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="o">...</span>

        <span class="c1"># е°ҶдёӨдёӘзҪ‘з»ңж”№еӣһ и®ӯз»ғеҪўејҸ
</span>        <span class="n">net_overfitting</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">net_dropped</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

